des:
Using AI and Walabot to unlock Peter's deadbolts, this is a skill that requires walabot radar as well as intel Up2 board, a full guide can be seen at https://www.hackster.io/Nyceane/ai-facial-recognition-lock-7a3e43

No account linking is needed, as this skill is an example of how to unlock Peter's deadbolt, you can look at the webcam to see his deadbolt unlocking, then build your own system accordingly.
